products.name: Japanese Maple Red
products.description: A stunning ornamental tree with deep red foliage that turns brilliant crimson in fall. Perfect focal point for any garden.

care.soil: Well-draining, slightly acidic, rich organic soil

products.name: Bird Of Paradise
products.description: Exotic tropical plant with striking orange and blue bird-like flowers. Perfect statement plant for patios and tropical gardens.

care.light: Full Sun to bright filtered light
care.water: Regular water, keep soil moist but not soggy
care.pruning: Remove dead leaves and spent flowers

products.name: Bougainvillea
products.description: Vibrant flowering vine with papery bracts in brilliant colors. Perfect for adding tropical flair to your landscape.
features: Can be trained as vine or shrub

care.light: Full Sun - needs intense light to bloom
care.water: Low to Moderate Water - drought tolerant
care.pruning: After flowering, can be pruned heavily
